net.tmachine.gpg4.gameserver
Interface iWritableSelectorHandler

All Superinterfaces:
iResponseWriter, iSelectorHandler
All Known Implementing Classes:
GatheringWritableSelectorHandler
public interface iWritableSelectorHandler
extends iSelectorHandler, iResponseWriter

Slightly lower lever than an iResponseWriter - this is an iResponseWriter that actually writes bytes to a channel, e.g. caches may implement iResponseWriter in order to proxy a real writer; implementations of this interface are "real" writers

See Also:
iResponseWriter, FourThreadWebserver
